				<td colspan="2"><span>some mobs are just not good for ae kiting. Grifs and all flying animals seem to  have long arms so to speak; it's easy to get out of range to hit them, while they can still hit you.  Try other mob types, if you were able to do Young Kods with CoD, you should be fine ae kiting but may need to change targets. Check out the hunting by level guides for ideas on level appropriate stuff. You should be ready Iceclad cougars if all you're looking for is fast exp.
