				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Advantages?<a name="55108"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 4 04 12:04 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Just an FYI Griffs fly at SoW speed.  That is likely the reason you will not be able to kite them efficiently.  I would say run over to Castle Mistmoore, and try those mobs (some are casters so careful).  Or head out to Marus Seru and AE kite there somewhere near the Sanctus Seru zoneline.  I think you could likely AE kite the shroom house in Dawnshroud peaks.  Easy to pull the train from there.  And Sanctus Seru isn't too far away.  The shroom hous is located along the zone edge between Greigs End, and Sanctus Seru  Can't miss it.  I would say give that a shot.  Once you clear the shrooms (fast repop) you can do Zels for a while till more shrooms are repopped.  EXP is excellent in DSP too.  Give it a try and lemme know how it worked for you.  I just melee soloed them, never even considered AE.  
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
